* BrightBlade looked over at Gangon as his movements caought her optic, 
groaning in the strain it took her head to move a bit.
She was glad to see that he wasn't all that damaged, but she wasn't exactly 
in the condition to celebrate.
She saw his wound but then narroed her optics, like she cared how little his 
would was. She was dying here!
Her voice was weak as she spoke.*

" I wish...I...could say...the...same."

* By now the entire floor of her cell was completely covered in her 
mech-fluid. Cursing the Maximals for not latting her had access to one of 
their chambers...at least!
And she wondered what was taking Perndabot so long, she had sent that 
message nearly half a mega-cycle ago.
BrightBlade moaned and turned her head slightly to look at the Maximal that 
was guarding them, trying to sneer at him agrily but ending up in one of 
pain.*
